<item>
            <title>[LU-15416] sanity-lfsck test_2e: TIMEOUT (osd_trans_exec_op ... opcode 7: before 241 &lt; left 408, rollback = 7)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15416</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for eaujames &amp;lt;eaujames@ddn.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/2da62c80-e8fa-4fbf-97d7-b0e97a62371f&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/2da62c80-e8fa-4fbf-97d7-b0e97a62371f&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_2e failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Timeout occurred after 139 mins, last suite running was sanity-lfsck
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue occurred on b2_12 branch (2.12.8..).&lt;br/&gt;
The following messages is displayed on MDS:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[Thu Dec 23 20:12:46 2021] Lustre: *** cfs_fail_loc=1603, val=0***
[Thu Dec 23 20:12:46 2021] Lustre: 22393:0:(osd_internal.h:1214:osd_trans_exec_op()) lustre-MDT0000: opcode 7: before 247 &amp;lt; left 408, rollback = 7
[Thu Dec 23 20:12:46 2021] Lustre: 22393:0:(osd_handler.c:1890:osd_trans_dump_creds())   create: 5/40/2, destroy: 0/0/0
[Thu Dec 23 20:12:46 2021] Lustre: 22393:0:(osd_handler.c:1897:osd_trans_dump_creds())   attr_set: 0/0/0, xattr_set: 2/106/2
[Thu Dec 23 20:12:46 2021] Lustre: 22393:0:(osd_handler.c:1907:osd_trans_dump_creds())   write: 11/408/0, punch: 0/0/0, quota 6/6/0
[Thu Dec 23 20:12:46 2021] Lustre: 22393:0:(osd_handler.c:1914:osd_trans_dump_creds())   insert: 11/201/5, delete: 0/0/0
[Thu Dec 23 20:12:46 2021] Lustre: 22393:0:(osd_handler.c:1921:osd_trans_dump_creds())   ref_add: 1/1/0, ref_del: 0/0/0
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The messages above are not shown when the test pass.&lt;br/&gt;
Is the journal target is too small to fit the transaction?&lt;/p&gt;





